### ============================================================
### 冷链后端 新功能接口测试（mock 模式）
### 使用方式：IDEA 中直接点每段前面的绿色箭头运行
### 前提：已启动 ColdChainBackendApplication（端口 18081）
### ============================================================

### 变量：登录后自动更新
@base = http://localhost:18081
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}


# ==================== 1. 认证接口 ====================

### 1.1 登录成功（admin / Admin123!）
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}


### 1.2 登录失败 — 密码错误
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "admin",
  "password": "wrong"
}


### 1.3 登录失败 — 账号封禁（zhaoliu 已被封禁）
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "zhaoliu",
  "password": "123456"
}


### 1.4 注册新用户
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "phone": "13811112222",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}


### 1.5 注册失败 — 用户名重复
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "phone": "13899990000",
  "email": "new@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}


### 1.6 获取当前用户（需先执行 1.1 登录）
GET {{base}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 1.7 退出登录
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


# ==================== 2. 后台管理接口（需先登录） ====================

### 2.1 后台聚合数据
GET {{base}}/api/v1/admin/console
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 2.2 修改用户角色/状态 — 将 operator 提升为管理员
PATCH {{base}}/api/v1/admin/users/USR-OPS-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "status": "启用中"
}


### 2.3 封禁用户
PATCH {{base}}/api/v1/admin/users/USR-202606030001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "USER",
  "status": "已封禁"
}


### 2.4 新增车辆
POST {{base}}/api/v1/admin/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "CC-VA-99",
  "cargoName": "疫苗",
  "status": "运输中",
  "driver": "测试司机",
  "route": "测试仓库 -> 测试医院"
}


### 2.5 编辑车辆
PUT {{base}}/api/v1/admin/vehicles/CC-VA-99
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "CC-VA-99",
  "cargoName": "血液制品",
  "status": "待命中",
  "driver": "测试司机2",
  "route": "新仓库 -> 新医院"
}


### 2.6 删除车辆
DELETE {{base}}/api/v1/admin/vehicles/CC-VA-99
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 2.7 更新告警处理状态
PATCH {{base}}/api/v1/admin/alerts/ALT-20260518-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "调度负责人",
  "level": "HIGH",
  "status": "已处理",
  "note": "已确认改道方案并通知司机执行"
}


### 2.8 无 Token 访问 — 应返回 401
GET {{base}}/api/v1/admin/console
